  "title": "Associate Engineer (Gantry) [Bedok | Shift work | up to $3150] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Gantry Associate Engineer </strong>(2 years contract renewable)</h3><p><strong>4 days, </strong><u><strong>12 hrs rotating shift</strong></u><strong> from 7-7; first few months </strong><u><strong>permanent night shift</strong></u><strong> from 8.30pm-6am</strong></p><p><strong>Currently the 4 days shift is spread from Monday to Saturday, 2 days off. Sunday is rotating standby.</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2800- $3150</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Bedok office </strong></p><p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>To perform comprehensive maintenance for system</li><li>To perform site supervision and hands on when required..</li><li>To perform troubleshooting and devise resolution when issues or faults arises.</li><li>To communicate/supervise contractors on safety and work related tasks.</li><li>To execute job related tasks assigned by Engineer/Shift Engineer.</li><li>To complete reports for jobs done.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li><strong>Diploma in Mechatronics, Electrical or Electronics</strong></li><li><strong>Willing to work at height (6 meters) on outdoor public road on gantries.</strong></li><li>Experience in electrical and electronic works.</li><li><strong>Class 3 driving license</strong> is required</li><li>Experience in basic Microsoft office.</li><li>Understand basic Window system.</li><li>Experience in site supervision work.</li><li>Understand in Mechanical/Electrical/Electronic system</li><li>Able to work in 12 hours rotating shift, first few months will be permanent night shifts</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
